рЯУД [32m Final Result:[0m 
Yes, you can track your order through the IKEA website. Go to the IKEA US site (https://www.ikea.com), scroll to the footer and click **My orders** (or directly visit https://www.ikea.com/us/en/customer-service/track-manage-order/). On the **Track and manage your order** page you will see a form where you need to enter:
- Your order number
- The email address or phone number used for the purchase (or log in with your IKEA Family account to see all orders)
After filling the fields, click the **Track order** button to view the status of your order.
The page also offers a **See all your orders** link for viewing your order history.
Thus, IKEA provides a straightforward online orderвАСtracking feature.


